name: Session Tracker
description:
Window to track different stats in your current gaming session for WvW, PvP and PvE. Stats can be:
- wallet currencies (gold, karma, volatile magic, fractal relics, wvw skirmish tickets, ...)
- deaths, PvP wins/losses, PvP and WvW kill/death-ratios, ...
- achievements (killed players in PvP/WvW, captured WvW towers, killed dolyaks, ...).
WARNING: The data is read from the official GW2 API with your API key and is therefore delayed. Expect delays of at least 5 minutes.
